{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 52,
    "name": "سُورَةُ الطُّورِ",
    "englishName": "At-Tur",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Mount",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 49,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 4736,
        "text": "By the Mount [Sinai],",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4737,
        "text": "by the Book inscribed",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4738,
        "text": "on an unrolled parchment;",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4739,
        "text": "by the House greatly frequented;",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4740,
        "text": "by the vault raised high,",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4741,
        "text": "by the surging sea:",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4742,
        "text": "indeed your Lord’s punishment will surely befall.",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4743,
        "text": "There is none who can avert it.",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4744,
        "text": "On the day when the sky whirls violently,",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4745,
        "text": "and the mountains move with an awful motion:",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4746,
        "text": "woe to the deniers on that day",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4747,
        "text": "—those who play around in vain talk,",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4748,
        "text": "the day when they will be shoved forcibly toward the fire of hell, [and told:]",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4749,
        "text": "‘This is the Fire which you used to deny!",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4750,
        "text": "Is this, then, [also] magic, or is it you who do not perceive?",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4751,
        "text": "Enter it, and it will be the same for you whether you are patient or impatient. You are only being requited for what you used to do.’",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4752,
        "text": "Indeed the Godwary will be amid gardens and bliss,",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4753,
        "text": "rejoicing because of what their Lord has given them, and that their Lord has saved them from the punishment of hell.",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4754,
        "text": "[They will be told:] ‘Enjoy your food and drink, [as a reward] for what you used to do.’",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4755,
        "text": "They will be reclining on arrayed couches, and We will wed them to big-eyed houris.",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4756,
        "text": "The faithful and their descendants who followed them in faith—We will make their descendants join them, and We will not stint anything from [the reward of] their deeds. Every person is hostage to what he has earned.",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4757,
        "text": "We will provide them with fruits and meat, such as they desire.",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4758,
        "text": "There they will pass from hand to hand a cup wherein there will be neither any vain talk nor sinful speech.",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4759,
        "text": "They will be waited upon by their youths, as if they were guarded pearls.",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4760,
        "text": "They will turn to one another, questioning each other.",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4761,
        "text": "They will say, ‘Indeed, aforetime, we used to be apprehensive about our families.",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4762,
        "text": "But Allah showed us favour and He saved us from the punishment of the [infernal] miasma.",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4763,
        "text": "We used to supplicate Him aforetime. Indeed He is the All-benign, the All-merciful.’",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4764,
        "text": "So admonish. By your Lord’s blessing, you are not a soothsayer, nor mad.",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4765,
        "text": "Do they say, ‘[He is] a poet, for whom we await a fatal accident’?",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4766,
        "text": "Say, ‘Wait! I too am waiting along with you.’",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4767,
        "text": "Is it their intellect which prompts them to [say] this, or are they a rebellious lot?",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4768,
        "text": "Do they say, ‘He has improvised it [himself]?’ Rather, they have no faith!",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4769,
        "text": "Let them bring a discourse like it, if they are truthful.",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4770,
        "text": "Were they created from nothing? Or are they [their own] creators?",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4771,
        "text": "Did they create the heavens and the earth? Rather, they have no certainty!",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4772,
        "text": "Do they possess the treasuries of your Lord? Or do they control [them]?",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4773,
        "text": "Do they have a ladder [leading up to heaven] whereby they eavesdrop? If so, let their eavesdropper produce a manifest authority.",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4774,
        "text": "Does He have daughters while you have sons?",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4775,
        "text": "Do you ask them for a reward, so that they are [wary of] being weighed down with debt?",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4776,
        "text": "Do they have [access to] the Unseen, which they write down?",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4777,
        "text": "Do they seek to outmaneuver [Allah]? But it is the faithless who are the outmaneuvered ones!",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4778,
        "text": "Do they have any god other than Allah? Clear is Allah of any partners that they may ascribe [to Him]!",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4779,
        "text": "Were they to see a fragment falling from the sky, they would say, ‘A cumulous cloud.’",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4780,
        "text": "So leave them until they encounter the day when they will be thunderstruck,",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4781,
        "text": "the day when their guile will not avail them in any way, nor will they be helped.",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4782,
        "text": "Indeed there is a punishment besides that for those who do wrong, but most of them do not know.",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4783,
        "text": "So submit patiently to the judgement of your Lord, for indeed you fare before Our eyes. And celebrate the praise of your Lord when you rise [at dawn],",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4784,
        "text": "and also glorify Him during the night and at the receding of the stars.",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
    "edition": {
